summary: Service booking app with admin panel. User wants to remove the 'actor not available' alert from the book service option, and add a contact number option to book service.

existing_features.title: Remove the 'actor not available' alert (or any similar error/warning dialog) that appears when a user attempts to use the Book Service option. The Book Service flow should remain accessible and functional without showing this blocking alert.
Add a 'Contact Number' input field to the Book Service form (Services.tsx). This field should allow users to provide a phone/contact number when submitting a service booking request.

new_feature_requests.summary: Remove 'actor not available' alert from the book service option
Add contact number option to the book service flow
